---
const painPoints = [
  {
    heading: 'Your staff are doing<br />robot work.',
    body: 'Every day, your team copies, pastes, chases, and checks the same things. By hand. That is not what you hired them for. That is not what they are good at. And every hour they spend on it is an hour not spent on work that actually grows your business.',
  },
  {
    heading: 'Things are falling through the gaps.',
    body: 'A missed email. A late invoice. A job that slipped through with no follow-up. It is not because your team is bad. It is because humans forget. The busier things get, the more gets dropped. And every dropped thing costs you money, or a customer.',
  },
  {
    heading: 'You cannot grow without hiring more people.',
    body: 'Every time the business gets busier, you need another pair of hands just to keep up. So the business grows but the profit does not. You are stuck — too busy to change anything, too stretched to scale properly. It does not have to work this way.',
  },
];
---

<section class="relative py-24 px-6 bg-brand-surface">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">

    <!-- Heading -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <p class="section-label">Sound familiar?</p>
      <h2 class="font-inter font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-brand-text leading-tight mb-6">
        Your business is busy.<br />But busy is not the same as working.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Pain point cards -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
      {painPoints.map((point) => (
        <div class="pain-card rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); backdrop-filter: blur(14px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(14px); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.80);">
          <!-- Card headline -->
          <h3 class="font-poppins font-semibold text-xl text-brand-accent mb-4 leading-snug" set:html={point.heading} />
          <!-- Card body -->
          <p class="font-inter text-brand-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
            {point.body}
          </p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- Closing statement -->
    <div class="border-t border-brand-surface3 pt-12">
      <p class="font-poppins font-semibold text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-text">
        The real cost is not the chaos.
        <span class="text-brand-accent"> It is the decisions you <span class="whitespace-nowrap">are making blind.</span></span>
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- Section transition gradient -->
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-20 pointer-events-none" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, #F0EDE8);"></div>
</section>

<style>
  .pain-card {
    transition: transform 0.22s ease, box-shadow 0.22s ease;
    cursor: default;
  }
  .pain-card:hover {
    transform: scale(1.025);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(45,27,142,0.35), 0 8px 32px rgba(45,27,142,0.10);
  }
</style>
